definitions.definition: A historical county in central Scotland , joined with Kinross-shire for administration after 1929.
The council area (or formerly the administrative county or district) of Perth and Kinross .

main_definition: A historical county in central Scotland , joined with Kinross-shire for administration after 1929.
secondary_definitions: ( from 1929 , informal ) The council area (or formerly the administrative county or district) of Perth and Kinross .
